# Installation

Using pip

`pip install drf_info_endpoint`

Using pipenv

`pipenv install drf_info_endpoint`

# Quick start
In your projectâ€™s `settings.py`.

```
DRF_INFO_ENDPOINT_PROJECT_NAME = "My Project"
DRF_INFO_ENDPOINT_VERSION = "v1.0"
```
